{"title":"iPhone与Windows传输文件的几种方式","date":"2022-01-22T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2022年1月22日","L":"2022/01/22","MM-DD":"01-22"},"thumbnail":"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67ac0f54cd3f937d1d763.png","link":"iPhone-Windows","tags":["Windows","iPhone"],"categories":["Windows","iPhone"],"updated":"2022-01-21T16:00:00.000Z","content":"<h3 id=\"创建文件夹\">创建文件夹<a title=\"#创建文件夹\" href=\"#创建文件夹\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>右键 <code>属性</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67304f54cd3f937ae8a7f.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>点击 <code>共享</code> 标签下的 <code>共享</code> 按钮, 选择 <code>Everyone</code>, 点击 <code>添加</code>, 最后点击 <code>共享</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67304f54cd3f937ae8a88.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>选择文件夹, 点击 <code>完成</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67304f54cd3f937ae8ac3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>继续点击 <code>高级共享</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67922f54cd3f937caab12.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>选中 <code>共享此文件夹</code>, 然后点击 <code>权限</code> 按钮</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67304f54cd3f937ae8ae3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>选中用户 <code>Everyone</code> 的读写权限, 然后一路确定</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67304f54cd3f937ae8afc.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>打开命令提示符工具, 输入: <code>ipconfig</code>, 找到自己电脑的IPv4 地址: <code>192.168.95.1</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d678e2f54cd3f937c98b45.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>打开手机软件 <code>文件</code>, 点击右上角: <code>连接服务器</code><br>\n<img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67947f54cd3f937cb45d4.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>输入上面获取到的IPv4 地址<br>\n<img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67947f54cd3f937cb45b0.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>输入电脑密码即可进入<br>\n<img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/62d67947f54cd3f937cb45e1.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"IP地址 归属地查询工具","link":"java-ip"},"next":{"title":"Centos 7 安装 Nginx - 配置 & 文件 & 说明","link":"nginx"},"plink":"http://l-zm.com/iPhone-Windows/","toc":[{"id":"创建文件夹","title":"创建文件夹","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"218 字约 1 分钟"}